OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright and
OL,6,Fwarm evening to end Monday, though any
OL,7,Flate sunshine may be rather hazy.
OL,8,FStaying dry overnight, though patchy
OL,9,Flow cloud may spread in to give some
OL,10,Fareas of mist. A mild night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FAny low cloud quickly lifting
OL,13,Fand breaking to bring a very warm day
OL,14,Fwith spells of strong sunshine and
OL,15,Flight winds. Fair-weather cloud
OL,16,Fdrifting through at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
